  "description": "<p>现在，传统相机制造商涉足“非相机”市场已经是公开的秘密。虽然越来越的人开始讨论拍照这件事儿，但大部分都不再将目光停留在相机上，而是智能手机。<strong>近日，尼康总裁木村真琴在接受彭博社的采访时透露，公司已经意识到了智能机当道的风潮，他们打算打造一款全新的产品来抢占这一市场。换句话说，尼康公司打算涉足非相机的领域中。</strong></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2ea04456/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244609.htm&amp;t=%E5%B0%BC%E5%BA%B7%E6%AC%B2%E6%89%93%E9%80%A0%E2%80%9C%E9%9D%9E%E7%9B%B8%E6%9C%BA%E2%80%9D%E4%BA%A7%E5%93%81+%E5%9C%A8%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E6%9C%BA%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%BA%E5%AF%BB%E6%89%BE%E7%94%9F%E5%AD%98%E6%9C%BA%E4%BC%9A\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244609.htm&amp;t=%E5%B0%BC%E5%BA%B7%E6%AC%B2%E6%89%93%E9%80%A0%E2%80%9C%E9%9D%9E%E7%9B%B8%E6%9C%BA%E2%80%9D%E4%BA%A7%E5%93%81+%E5%9C%A8%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E6%9C%BA%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%BA%E5%AF%BB%E6%89%BE%E7%94%9F%E5%AD%98%E6%9C%BA%E4%BC%9A\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244609.htm&amp;t=%E5%B0%BC%E5%BA%B7%E6%AC%B2%E6%89%93%E9%80%A0%E2%80%9C%E9%9D%9E%E7%9B%B8%E6%9C%BA%E2%80%9D%E4%BA%A7%E5%93%81+%E5%9C%A8%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E6%9C%BA%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%BA%E5%AF%BB%E6%89%BE%E7%94%9F%E5%AD%98%E6%9C%BA%E4%BC%9A\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244609.htm&amp;t=%E5%B0%BC%E5%BA%B7%E6%AC%B2%E6%89%93%E9%80%A0%E2%80%9C%E9%9D%9E%E7%9B%B8%E6%9C%BA%E2%80%9D%E4%BA%A7%E5%93%81+%E5%9C%A8%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E6%9C%BA%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%BA%E5%AF%BB%E6%89%BE%E7%94%9F